{
  "stem": "1387.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He went to, to the village to retrieve some of the materials-- some of the goods that his father left with the local population.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they killed him, and they dismembered his body.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "After that, the winters came, and it was difficult to find a place where to sleep at night, although we walked most of the time in the woods in the snow till I was found by a man by the name of Milyg Zilber.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Milyg Zilber was a friend of mine from Zloczow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He, himself, was a son of a very wealthy man in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] He was lucky to be in a bunker that a family, Szarf, built.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were local people from the village, from, from [NON-ENGLISH] and from [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they knew the area quite well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The woods, they know it very well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they never went to, to a ghetto or to a camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They went from their homes into the woods, and they build themself a beautiful bunker.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And he was, he was able to persuade these people, the Szarf family, to take me in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] All I can tell you is when I got there, I had to be outside the bunker until they let me in because I was full of lice.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So after they were able to clean me up--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was kerosene.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They washed me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took the clothes, and they boiled it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they-- after a few days, they were able to get rid of it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, well, I stayed in that bunker, and that was like being at the Waldorf Astoria.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- they had food there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had a stove.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Over 20 people survived in that bunker.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a large bunker.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
